         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Collection consists of 2,400, 35 mm color slides of various topics of Canadian art, culture, and history. Produce for classroom use by the National Museum of Man and the National Film Board of Canada, Ottawa. Accompanying information booklets in English and French.</p>  
